    "description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/78deb4e636958d06ebcfc342ca64c452.poster.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/78deb4e636958d06ebcfc342ca64c452.webm?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/78deb4e636958d06ebcfc342ca64c452.mp4?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/f2453a9dc13f83a4dc8303885c93a5bc.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/563cf53b9568195e9d5dd8adb96a6e42.poster.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/563cf53b9568195e9d5dd8adb96a6e42.webm?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/563cf53b9568195e9d5dd8adb96a6e42.mp4?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>运用策略性连锁反应，向朋友发动致命进攻。坚持下去，获得最高分数赢得对战！<br><br>寻求挑战？在故事模式中使用独特游戏机制痛扁特殊首领！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/eed216c5b42a40d7f7e76848a0ad2212.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/3138b360b8b0c9a34d7f960086b6bd07.poster.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/3138b360b8b0c9a34d7f960086b6bd07.webm?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/3138b360b8b0c9a34d7f960086b6bd07.mp4?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在本款策略游戏中：使用连击越多，获得分数越高。成为最佳驱魔师，找到个人风格，尝试不同难度关卡，解锁角色、背景，还有更多待玩家发掘。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/2388d2c4e6e812e6f193ce508dde8bfa.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/06119698e70a28ba0dda63ae909125c4.poster.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/06119698e70a28ba0dda63ae909125c4.webm?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/06119698e70a28ba0dda63ae909125c4.mp4?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>12 位精彩角色可供选择，每位角色都有个人独一无二的能力，在本地模式或 Steam Remote Play 中最多可实现四人同时对战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/8ce1493d691709d3ef16c5e25b3ee9a0.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/ecf8dbf1234957941df010d066d4b8cc.poster.avif?t=1695914839\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/ecf8dbf1234957941df010d066d4b8cc.webm?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812170/extras/ecf8dbf1234957941df010d066d4b8cc.mp4?t=1695914839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>隔开灵界与现实世界之间的壁垒正岌岌可危！蛋蛋鬼在全岛四处出现，开始威胁到岛上得之不易的宁静生活。加入驱魔学院，解开谜团，成为最佳蛋蛋鬼猎手！<br><br>",
